node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by FactsofHealth™ on July 19, 2021 tagging @cnn. May be an image of text that says 'LIVE TV CNN health An epidemic in the shadow of a pandemic: Drug overdose deaths reach an all-time high in US By Sarah Braner, CNN Updated 1:17 PM ET, Sat July 17, 2021 09'.

node.text:
An epidemic in the shadow of a pandemic: Drug overdose deaths reach an all-time high in US

More than 93,000 people died from a drug overdose last year, according to provisional data from the US Centers for Disease Control and Prevention's National Center for Health Statistics.

This means that 2020 was the deadliest year on record for drug overdoses.

(Via: CNN)

MAKE SURE YOUR FRIENDS ARE AWARE!

node.text:
With Summer just around the corner I wanted to give you some tips on picking the perfect ripe watermelon. Dry weathering spots and vein like webbing are indicators of a sweet watermelon the spots are where the sugar has been seeping out of the fruit. The field spot should be creamy and yellow not white. Give it a good tap the sound should be hollow meaning it has more water. Lastly pick the heavy one for its size because it has more water content. #watermelon #watermelonsugar #watermelonjuice #howtopickawatermelon #healthyfood #fruithacks #eatarainbow #healthysnacks #healthysnackideas #naturescandy

Credit: @myhealthydish
